cn.campusapp.pan.autorender

类 AutoRenderViewModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • cn.campusapp.pan.GeneralViewModel
      • cn.campusapp.pan.autorender.AutoRenderViewModel
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    AutoRender, FactoryViewModel, ViewModel

    public abstract class AutoRenderViewModel
extends GeneralViewModel
implements AutoRender
    Automatically trigger render on particular lifecycle status:
    1. Activity.onResume/Fragment.onResume
    2. Fragment.setUserVisibleHint(true)
    Configure it using autoRender() and autoRender(boolean)

    Created by nius on 10/13/15.
